title: KeepVid Pro 7.0.1.2 Multilingual_Activator
description:
Ultimate Video Downloader to Download Videos from YouTube and 10,000 Other Sites Quickly and Easily. Download videos from YouTube and more than 10,000 other video sharing sites, including Dailymotion, Hulu, Break, Metacafe, BlipTV, Vimeo, AOL, Lynda, MegaVideo, Veoh, VideoBash, LiveLeak, MyVideo, FunnyOrDie, Nico Video, TV.com, Veevr, Adobe TV and more.	


Download Videos in Any Format
KeepVid Pro not only downloads videos as-is in MP4, 3GP, FLV, WebM formats, but also downloads videos to any other format with just one click. It supports more than 150 formats, like AVI, MKV, WMV, iPhone, PSP, Android, etc.
Download YouTube Playlists & Lynda Playlists in Batch
KeepVid Pro enables you to download an entire playlist or channel in just one click from YouTube and Lynda websites. All the videos in the playlist can be downloaded at one time. Adding up to 5000 download tasks for each time is so easy.
Ultra-Fast Download Speed with Turbo Mode
With multi-thread technology, KeepVid Pro enables you to download videos with 3X Faster speed compared with common downloaders.
Record Videos from Online Sites or Record Desktop Screen
KeepVid Pro is a splendid video recorder to capture videos from any online streaming sites or record the desktop activities on your computer.
Capture videos from any online sites
Capture streaming videos, online videos & TV shows from any sites, like Netflix, Hulu, BBC etc. You can also record live videos simultaneously.
Capture videos from computer screen
Capture the program window, specific part of the screen, or the full screen by adjusting the capture area. So you can record Skype calls for playback, create tutorial videos, capture and share your splendid game moments.
Capture videos with no more waiting
Set the end time for capturing at any time duration automatically. You can free yourself from waiting for the whole recording process.
Convert Local/Downloaded/Recorded Videos to Any Format
KeepVid Pro converts online videos or local videos to 150+ different formats and various multimedia devices, including MP4, AVI, MPG, MKV, WMV, M4V, MOV, iPhone, iPad, and more
